               <msContents>
                  <summary>Conclusion of a petition, probably addressed to the epistrategos, following Zoilos' signature and date is the signed bill of indictment of the epistrategos.</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Margins: left, 2.5 cm.; right, 0.3 cm.; bottom, 5.4 cm.; in bottom right corner, in red ink: 439; on verso, in black ink: T 246.</note>
                     <note type="general">14th year of the Emperor Antoninus Pius, the 21st of the Egyptian month Payni.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="grc">Greek</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc>
                     <supportDesc>
