                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <ab type="lines">15 lines, on recto along the fibers.</ab>
                           <ab type="recto-verso">Verso empty.</ab>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                     <p>3 different hands: 1 (lines 1-12), body of petition and date: regular cursive; 2 (line 15), date: small semi-uncials; 3 (lines 16-17), subscription of official: dark semi-uncials.</p>
